OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,FMelania Trump has blasted what she
OL,8,Fcalled the "lies" linking her to
OL,9,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein,
OL,10,Fsaying "the stories are completely
OL,11,Ffalse" and "need to end".
OL,13,FSpeaking at the White House, the
OL,14,FUnited States first lady called online
OL,15,Faccusations about her association with
OL,16,Fthe convicted sex offender "false
OL,17,Fsmears" from "mean-spirited"
OL,18,Findividuals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
