OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775775781
OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,F"The lies linking me with the
OL,8,Fdisgraceful Jeffrey Epstein need to
OL,9,Fend today. The individuals lying about
OL,10,Fme are devoid of ethical standards,
OL,11,Fhumility and respect. I do not object
OL,12,Fto their ignorance, but rather I
OL,13,Freject their mean-spirited attempts to
OL,14,Fdefame my reputation," she said.
OL,16,F"The false smears about me from mean-
OL,17,Fspirited and politically motivated
OL,18,Findividuals and entities looking to
OL,19,Fcause damage to my good name to gain
OL,20,Ffinancially and climb politically must
OL,21,Fstop.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@VO]xD@AOU
