OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,F"I have never been friends with
OL,8,FEpstein. Donald and I were invited to
OL,9,Fthe same parties as Epstein from time
OL,10,Fto time, since overlapping in social
OL,11,Fcircles is common in New York City and
OL,12,FPalm Beach. To be clear, I never had a
OL,13,Frelationship with Epstein or his
OL,14,Faccomplice, (Ghislaine) Maxwell."
OL,16,FShe described an email reply she sent
OL,17,Fto Maxwell as "casual correspondence"
OL,18,Fwithout elaborating. "My polite reply
OL,19,Fto her email doesn't amount to
OL,20,Fanything more than a trifle," she said.
