OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,FIn the extraordinary statement, Ms
OL,8,FTrump called for Congress to hold a
OL,9,Fpublic hearing centred on the
OL,10,Fsurvivors of Epstein's crimes, with a
OL,11,Fchance to testify before lawmakers and
OL,12,Fhave their stories entered into the
OL,13,Fcongressional record.
OL,15,F"Each and every woman should have her
OL,16,Fday to tell her story in public if she
OL,17,Fwishes," she said. "Then, and only
OL,18,Fthen, we will have the truth."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@HO]yD@TOUzD@^O]
