OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,FMs Trump said she had "fought" against
OL,8,Fthe rumours, alongside her attornies,
OL,9,Fsaying she will "continue to maintain
OL,10,Fmy sound reputation."
OL,12,F"I am not Epstein's victim, Epstein
OL,13,Fdid not introduce me to Donald Trump.
OL,14,FI met my husband by chance at the New
OL,15,FYork City Party in 1998. This initial
OL,16,Fencounter with my husband is
OL,17,Fdocumented in a detail in my book,
OL,18,FMelania," she said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
