OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,F"The first time I crossed paths with
OL,8,FEpstein was in the year 2000 at an
OL,9,Fevent Donald and I attended together.
OL,10,FAt the time, I had never met Epstein
OL,11,Fand had no knowledge of his criminal
OL,12,Fundertakings.
OL,14,F"Numerous fake images and statements
OL,15,Fabout Epstein and me have been
OL,16,Fcirculating on social media for years
OL,17,Fnow. Be cautious about what you
OL,18,Fbelieve these images and stories are
OL,19,Fcompletely false."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
