OL,3,CMelania Trump blasts 'lies' linking
OL,4,Cher to Epstein in rare White House
OL,5,Cstatement
OL,7,FHer rare statement came just as her
OL,8,Fhusband, President Donald Trump, and
OL,9,Fhis administration had finally
OL,10,Fappeared successful in moving beyond
OL,11,Fthe Epstein controversy, which had
OL,12,Fsent shockwaves through the nation's
OL,13,Fpolitics for months.
OL,15,FPresident Trump and his cabinet have
OL,16,Fsought to downplay Epstein and his
OL,17,Fvictims, repeatedly and publicly
OL,18,Fstating that the country is ready to
OL,19,Fmove on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
